Tie/Scalar/Escaped version 0.01
===============================

At FETCH time, some transformations are performed
on the data in the scalar so it is expanded to only
include characters in [0-9a-z%].


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

"pure perl"

